# Local Fastlane configuration. Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and fill
# in real values; the Makefile's `fl-*` targets source this file.
#
# Do NOT commit the real .env or the .p8 key. The .p8 lives outside
# the repo entirely (DOLL-155).

# App Store Connect API key — generate at
#   https://appstoreconnect.apple.com/access/integrations/api
# and store the .p8 OUTSIDE this repo. Recommended path:
#   ~/Library/Application Support/com.dollhousemediatech.blackbox/keys/AuthKey_<KEY_ID>.p8
ASC_KEY_ID="<your-key-id>"
ASC_ISSUER_ID="<your-issuer-id>"
ASC_KEY_PATH="$HOME/Library/Application Support/com.dollhousemediatech.blackbox/keys/AuthKey_<your-key-id>.p8"

# Apple Developer Team ID (overrides the Appfile fallback).
# Empty / unset is fine — the Fastfile reads from
# BlackBoxApp/fastlane/Appfile when this is missing (DOLL-151).
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM=""
